'''闊里吉思'''（{{bd|？||1298年}}），[[元朝|元朝]][[蒙古|蒙古]][[汪古部|汪古部]]首领，爱不花之子，為元朝駙馬，封[[高唐王|高唐王]]。他尚文武，雖信奉[[景教|景教]]，卻好儒学，在私宅有万卷堂，常和儒生讨论经史。<ref>{{cite book |author=蕭啓慶 |date=2012 |title=《九州四海風雅同：元代多族士人圈的形成與發展》 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=odRFBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA115&lpg=PA115&dq=%E9%97%8A%E9%87%8C%E5%90%89%E6%80%9D+%E6%99%AF%E6%95%99&source=bl&ots=FDEkiD2Sr8&sig=ACfU3U1gEl9uQiBvdsvyMU-z9sI0GI1-ZQ&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwi56O2Mo8jgAhUJ1eAKHU3RDaU4ChDoATABegQICBAB#v=onepage&q=%E9%97%8A%E9%87%8C%E5%90%89%E6%80%9D%20%E6%99%AF%E6%95%99&f=false |location=新北市 |publisher=聯經出版 |page={{p.|115}} |isbn=9789860327946 |author-link=蕭啟慶 |access-date=2019-02-19 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713033752/https://books.google.com/books?id=odRFBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA115&lpg=PA115&dq=%E9%97%8A%E9%87%8C%E5%90%89%E6%80%9D+%E6%99%AF%E6%95%99&source=bl&ots=FDEkiD2Sr8&sig=ACfU3U1gEl9uQiBvdsvyMU-z9sI0GI1-ZQ&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwi56O2Mo8jgAhUJ1eAKHU3RDaU4ChDoATABegQICBAB#v=onepage&q=%E9%97%8A%E9%87%8C%E5%90%89%E6%80%9D%20%E6%99%AF%E6%95%99&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>後在義大利傳教士[[若望·孟高維諾|若望·孟高維諾]]勸說下改宗[[天主教會|天主教]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.radiovaticana.va/cinesebig5/churchistory/orme/orme09.html |title=華夏史上的福音蹤跡：九、汗八里及刺桐教區的教務發展 |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |website=[[梵蒂岡新聞網|radiovaticana.va]] |access-date=2019-02-19 |archive-date=2019-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220062833/http://www.radiovaticana.va/cinesebig5/churchistory/orme/orme09.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>「闊里吉思」（{{lang|syr-Latn|Giwargis}}）一名原本就是來自基督教聖名「[[聖喬治|喬治]]」（{{lang|en|George}}），<ref>{{cite book |last=Winkler |first=Dietmar W. |date=2016 |title=''Syrische Studien'' |trans-title= |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4DKSDQAAQBAJ&pg=PA230&lpg=PA230&dq=%E9%97%8A%E9%87%8C%E5%90%89%E6%80%9D+Giwargis&source=bl&ots=C01d8wavrd&sig=ACfU3U0VYvKYbbkFxJG5XQjmVAqHYaowyg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjMwfWqqMjgAhVD2OAKHa7rBuQQ6AEwB3oECAkQAQ#v=onepage&q=%E9%97%8A%E9%87%8C%E5%90%89%E6%80%9D%20Giwargis&f=false |language=en |location=Münster |publisher=LIT Verlag |page={{p.|230}} |isbn=9783643507433 |access-date=2019-02-19 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713033752/https://books.google.com/books?id=4DKSDQAAQBAJ&pg=PA230&lpg=PA230&dq=%E9%97%8A%E9%87%8C%E5%90%89%E6%80%9D+Giwargis&source=bl&ots=C01d8wavrd&sig=ACfU3U0VYvKYbbkFxJG5XQjmVAqHYaowyg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjMwfWqqMjgAhVD2OAKHa7rBuQQ6AEwB3oECAkQAQ#v=onepage&q=%E9%97%8A%E9%87%8C%E5%90%89%E6%80%9D%20Giwargis&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>因此他在歐洲被稱為喬治王。

他先娶[[忽必烈|忽必烈]]皇太子[[真金|真金]]的女儿忽答的迷失。后来娶[[元成宗|元成宗]]女爱牙失里。开始受命屯驻[[和林|和林]]，防御[[海都|海都]]。1287年，率领一千骑兵讨伐[[乃颜|乃颜]]同党也不-{干}-<ref>也不-{干}-，人名。</ref>，过[[土拉河|土拉河]]，胜利受赏。1292年，和[[耶律希亮|耶律希亮]]在合敦奴孙界商议实行屯田，元成宗封他为高唐王。因为海都、[[笃哇|笃哇]]之乱未平，他自请讨伐。在伯牙思大败敌军。1298年，击败笃哇、[[彻彻秃|彻彻秃]]三次进攻，乘胜追击，但是孤军无援，最终被俘虏杀害。1305年，追封'''[[赵王|赵王]]'''。立《[[驸马|驸马]][[高唐王|高唐]]忠献王[[碑|碑]]》纪念。

==DNA==
据吉林大学边疆考古研究中心在2014年的研究，[[梳妆楼|梳妆楼]]墓地之汪古部[[高唐王|高唐王]]阔里吉思遗骨检测结果{{link-en|Y-DNA haplogroup Q-M242|Haplogroup Q-M242}}<ref>Yinqiu, Cui et al. 2015, Identification of kinship and occupant status in Mongolian noble burials of the Yuan Dynasty through a multidisciplinary approach, Phil. Trans. R. Soc. B370:20130378, http://dx.doi.org/10.1098/rstb.2013.0378 {{Wayback|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1098/rstb.2013.0378 |date=20190713033752 }}</ref>。大致上可以断定汪古部的贵族属单倍群Q-M242，单倍群Q-M242在[[中美洲|中]]、[[南美洲|南美洲]]的印第安人群中出现的频率最高，<ref name="Bortolini2003">{{cite journal|doi=10.1086/377588|title=Y-Chromosome Evidence for Differing Ancient Demographic Histories in the Americas|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-human-genetics_2003-09_73_3/page/524|year=2003|last1=Bortolini|first1=M|last2=Salzano|first2=F|last3=Thomas|first3=M|last4=Stuart|first4=S|last5=Nasanen|first5=S|last6=Bau|first6=C|last7=Hutz|first7=M|last8=Layrisse|first8=Z|last9=Petzlerler|first9=M|last10=Tsuneto|first10=L|last11=Hill|first11=K|last12=Hurtado|first12=A. M.|last13=Castro-De-Guerra|first13=D|last14=Torres|first14=M. M.|last15=Groot|first15=H|last16=Michalski|first16=R|last17=Nymadawa|first17=P|last18=Bedoya|first18=G|last19=Bradman|first19=N|last20=Labuda|first20=D|last21=Ruiz-Linares|first21=A|journal=The American Journal of Human Genetics|volume=73|issue=3|pages=524–39|pmid=12900798|pmc=1180678|display-authors=8}}</ref>也有一部分的[[北美洲|北美洲]]印第安人群有此单倍群，单倍群Q-M242出现的频率在[[爱斯基摩人|爱斯基摩人]]、[[阿留申人|阿留申人]]中也很高。<ref name=”Zegura2004”>{{cite journal|author=Zegura SL, Karafet TM, Zhivotovsky LA, Hammer MF|title=High-resolution SNPs and microsatellite haplotypes point to a single, recent entry of Native American Y-chromosomes into the Americas|journal=Mol. Biol. Evol.|volume=21|issue=1|pages=164–75|date=January 2004|pmid=14595095|doi=10.1093/molbev/msh009|url=http://mbe.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/reprint/21/1/164.pdf|access-date=2016-12-02|archive-date=2008-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080906204641/http:/